code: import axios from"axios";var SERVER='http://127.0.0.1:8002/api/event';var headers={'Content-Type':'application/json','Authorization':'JWT fefege..'};function taskAPI(data){return axios.get("".concat(SERVER,"/date/").concat(data.date));}function completeAPI(data){return axios.post("".concat(SERVER,"/complete/").concat(data.id),{completion:data.completion},{headers:headers});}function addTaskAPI(data){return axios.post("".concat(SERVER,"/create"),data,{headers:headers});}function deleteTaskAPI(data){return axios.delete("".concat(SERVER,"/delete/").concat(data.id));}export default{taskAPI:taskAPI,completeAPI:completeAPI,addTaskAPI:addTaskAPI,deleteTaskAPI:deleteTaskAPI};
